State ex rel. Barrett
v.
Byrd 2018-0689 Supreme Court of Ohio. June 26, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

In Prohibition. On relator's application for dismissal. Application granted. Cause dismissed. Relator's "request for a stay of the collect of cost or fees owed at the appellate court level until relator has obtained a waiver in the court of appeals of cost or fees in case no. 106823" denied.
